'''弗萊比航空'''（{{lang-en|'''Flybe'''}}）是英國一家[[低成本航空公司|低成本]]的地區航空公司，總部位於[[伯明翰|伯明翰]]，以[[贝尔法斯特城市機場|贝尔法斯特城市機場]]和[[伯明翰國際機場|伯明翰國際機場]]作為樞紐。<ref>"[http://www.flybe.com/contact/default.htm Contact Us] {{Wayback|url=http://www.flybe.com/contact/default.htm |date=20150924013910 }}." Flybe. Retrieved on 29 August 2009. "Customer Call Centre Flybe Customer Call Centre Jack Walker House Exeter International Airport Devon EX5 2HL United Kingdom"</ref> 弗莱比航空一度有著102個航點，也是歐洲最大的地區航空公司，持有[[民用航空管理局_(英國)|民用航空管理局]]的A類運營許可證<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.caa.co.uk/default.aspx?categoryid=183&pagetype=90&pageid=340 |title=Operating Licence |publisher=Caa.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2014-01-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070311005729/http://www.caa.co.uk/default.aspx?categoryid=183&pagetype=90&pageid=340 |archivedate=2007-03-11 }}</ref>。2020年3月5日一度倒闭，但于2022年重新开业。

==历史==
該公司創立於1979年，當時稱澤西歐洲航空公司（Jersey European Airways），後來改名英國歐洲航空公司（British European），再後來改現名。2007年收購{{Tsl|en|BA Connect|BA Connect}}組成弗萊比集團。2019年1月11日，[[維珍航空|維珍航空]]等组成的财团联合航空（Connect Airways）宣布将收购弗莱比<ref name="fg-20190111">{{cite news |last1=Kaminski-Morrow |first1=David |title=Virgin Atlantic and Stobart link up to take over Flybe |url=https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/virgin-atlantic-and-stobart-link-up-to-take-over-fly-454952/ |work=Flightglobal |date=11 January 2019 |accessdate=2020-04-25 |archive-date=2019-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191014150432/https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/virgin-atlantic-and-stobart-link-up-to-take-over-fly-454952/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2月21日交易完成<ref name=cityam-20190221>{{cite news |last1=Warrington |first1=James |title=Flybe completes sale to Virgin-led consortium |url=http://www.cityam.com/273638/flybe-completes-sale-virgin-led-consortium-after-dramatic |work=cityam.com |date=21 February 2019 |accessdate=2020-04-25 |archive-date=2019-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222042206/http://www.cityam.com/273638/flybe-completes-sale-virgin-led-consortium-after-dramatic |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年10月，公司宣布将在2020年初改名为维珍联合（Virgin Connect）<ref name="VC1">{{cite press release |url= https://virginconnect.co.uk/ |title= Our Journey to Virgin Connect |publisher= Virgin Connect |date= 15 October 2019 |access-date= 2020-04-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191015161837/https://virginconnect.co.uk/ |archive-date= 2019-10-15 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

2020年初，由於[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]在歐洲的肆虐，業務大受影響。3月5日，因政府没有批准其1亿英镑贷款，公司宣佈破產，停止所有经营活动。<ref>{{cite news |title=肺炎疫情中英國迎來三個第一：本土死亡，確診過百，航空公司倒閉 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-51756723 |accessdate=2020-03-08 |work=BBC |date=2020-03-05|archive-date=2020-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200424125218/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-51756723 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Flight5march2020>{{cite news |url= https://www.flightglobal.com/airlines/beleaguered-flybe-ceases-operations/137095.article |title= Beleaguered Flybe ceases operations |author= Alfred Chua |date= 2020-03-05 |work= Flightglobal |accessdate= 2020-04-25 |archive-date= 2020-04-28 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200428064936/https://www.flightglobal.com/airlines/beleaguered-flybe-ceases-operations/137095.article |dead-url= no }}</ref>

2021年11月，公司宣布选择[[伯明翰机场|伯明翰机场]]作为其新总部所在地（之前位于[[埃克塞特|埃克塞特]]）<ref name=flight17112021>{{cite news |last1=Perry |first1=Dominic |title=Flybe picks Birmingham as first UK base and HQ |url=https://www.flightglobal.com/airlines/flybe-picks-birmingham-as-first-uk-base-and-hq/146469.article |work=Flight Global |date=17 November 2021 |language=en |accessdate=2022-03-31 |archive-date=2021-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211118100351/https://www.flightglobal.com/airlines/flybe-picks-birmingham-as-first-uk-base-and-hq/146469.article }}</ref>。2022年3月16日，公司宣布将在下周重新开始售票<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bodell |first1=Luke |title=The New Flybe Will Launch Ticket Sales Next Week |url=https://simpleflying.com/new-flybe-launch-ticket-sales-next-week/ |work=Simple Flying |date=17 March 2022 |accessdate=2022-03-31 |archive-date=2022-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220317084842/https://simpleflying.com/new-flybe-launch-ticket-sales-next-week/ }}</ref>，3月22日网站开始重新售票，第一班航班位于4月13日<ref>{{cite news |last1=Collis |first1=Emily |title=Full list of new Flybe routes from Brum with flights from £19.99 |url=https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/travel/flybe-routes-birmingham-airport-full-23461690 |work=BirminghamLive |date=22 March 2022 |accessdate=2022-03-31 |archive-date=2022-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412214242/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/travel/flybe-routes-birmingham-airport-full-23461690 }}</ref>。

